st enduringly popular girls' names."],"variants":[{"name":"Sara","meanings":["Variant of   Sarah .  This is the form used in the Greek of the New Testament (Hebrews 11:11)."]}]}],"lifeSummary":"Sarah was born about 1570, in Kent, England, United Kingdom. She married Gregory Henley on 16 October 1614, in Appledore, Kent, England, United Kingdom. They were the parents of at least 1 daughter. She died about 1614, at the age of 46, and was buried in Tenterden, Kent, England, United Kingdom."},"et":{"abt 1570–abt 1614":"umbes 1570–umbes 1614","1570–1618":"1570–1618","1592–1618":"1592–1618","1570–1614":"1570–1614","abt 1614":"umbes 1614","abt 1570":"umbes 1570","1592":"1592","1570":"1570","1618":"1618","14 Jun 1614":"14. juuni 1614","1614":"1614","Tenterden, Kent, England":"Tenterden, Kent, Inglismaa, United Kingdom","Tenderden, Kent, England":"Kent, Inglismaa, United Kingdom"},"fi":{"abt 1570–abt 1614":"noin 1570–noin 1614","1570–1618":"1570–1618","1592–1618":"1592–1618","1570–1614":"1570–1614","abt 1614":"noin 1614","abt 1570":"noin 1570","1592":"1592","1570":"1570","1618":"1618","14 Jun 1614":"14. kesäkuuta 1614","1614":"1614","Tenterden, Kent, England":"Tenterden, Kent, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta","Tenderden, Kent, England":"Kent, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta"},"fr":{"abt 1570–abt 1614":"environ 1570–environ 1614","1570–1618":"1570–1618","1592–1618":"1592–1618","1570–1614":"1570–1614","abt 1614":"environ 1614","abt 1570":"environ 1570","1592":"1592","1570":"1570","1618":"1618","14 Jun 1614":"14 juin 1614","1614":"1614","Tenterden, Kent, England":"Tenterden, Kent, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni","Tenderden, Kent, England":"Kent, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni","lifeSummary":"Sarah est née environ 1570, à Kent, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni. Elle a épousé Gregory Henley le 16 octobre 1614, à Appledore, Kent, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni. Ils ont eu au moins 1 fille. Elle est décédée environ 1614, à l’âge de 46 ans, et a été enterrée à Tenterden, Kent, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni."},"d